data.text:
Roland-Rainer-Platz 1

James Newton Howard is one of the most successful and well-known film music composers in the world. In the concert series "The best of 30 years of Hollywood" the audience will experience the highlights of his career with music, film contributions and exciting stories. James Newton Howard will direct a symphony orchestra with a choir of over 100 artists.
